creen Couple|Best onscreen Couple]] \u2013 Jury; with [[Sanam Saeed]]\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[Hum Award for Best Onscreen Couple Popular|Best onscreen Couple \u2013 Popular]]; with [[Sanam Saeed]]\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Lux Style Awards\n| Best Television Actor \u2013 Satellite\n| {{won}}\n|<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.dawn.com/news/1148962|title=Winners announced for 2014 Lux Style Awards|last=Mahjabeen|first=Makhani|work=Dawn|date=5 December 2014|accessdate=29 September 2017|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170728160153/https://www.dawn.com/news/1148962|archivedate=28 July 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| Masala! Awards\n| Best Bollywood Debut\n\n!scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"4\" |''[[Khoobsurat (2014 film)|Khoobsurat]]''\n| {{won}}\n|<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.dawn.com/news/1147289|title=Fawad Khan wins 'Best Bollywood Debut' at Masala Awards 2014|work=Dawn|date=29 November 2014|accessdate=29 September 2017|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170929135603/https://www.dawn.com/news/1147289|archivedate=29 September 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[BIG Star Entertainment Awards]]\n| Most Entertaining Actor (Film) Debut \u2013 Male\n| {{won}}\n|<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.ibtimes.co.in/big-star-entertainment-awards-2014-live-streaming-information-complete-winners-list-618806|title=Big Star Entertainment Awards 2014: Live Streaming Information and Complete Winners List|work=IBT India|date=31 December 2014|accessdate=23 June 2018|url-status=live|archivedate=13 December 2017|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171213050705/https://www.ibtimes.co.in/big-star-entertainment-awards-2014-live-streaming-information-complete-winners-list-618806}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" | 2015\n| [[Producers Guild Film Awards|Star Guild Awards]]\n| Most Promising Debut (Male)\n| {{nom}}\n|<ref>{{cite news|publisher=NDTV|url=http://movies.ndtv.com/bollywood/star-guild-awards-2015-queen-pk-lead-nominations-724735|title=Star Guild Awards 2015: Queen, PK Lead Nominatio