t of Law of the Jungle episodes#Patagonia|in Patagonia]]''\n|SBS\n|Episode 305\u2013310. Part of second-half cast member.\n|-\n|''Sea Police'' || [[MBC Every1]] || Main cast\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2019 || ''[[Urban Cops]]'' || [[MBC Every1]] || Main cast\n|-\n|''[[Coffee Friends]]''|| [[TVN (South Korea)|tvN]] || Guest (Episodes 2-5,8-10)  <ref>[http://news.mk.co.kr/newsRead.php?year=2019&no=9143 \"\uc870\uc7ac\uc724, \u2018\ucee4\ud53c\ud504\ub80c\uc988\u2019 \uc5f4\ud608 \uc54c\ubc14\uc0dd \ubcc0\uc2e0 \u201c\uae30\ub300\ud574 \uc8fc\uc138\uc6a9\u201d\"] [M+\u2605SNS] (in Korean). 5 January 2019.</ref>\n|}\n\n==Theater==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year \n! Title\n! Role\n! Reprised\n|-\n| || ''The Magic Wings'' || || \n|-\n| || ''The Stepping Stone'' || || \n|-\n| || ''[[Linie 1|Subway Line 1]]'' || ||\n|-\n| || ''[[The Tempest]]'' || || \n|-\n| 2004 || ''[[The Human Comedy (musical)|The Human Comedy]]'' || Grandfather/Detective/Dancer || 2007-2008, <br/> 2008-2009, <br/> 2013\n|-\n| 2007 || ''[[The Bald Soprano]]'' || Fire chief || 2011\n|-\n| 2013 || ''[[University of Laughs]]'' || Censor || 2014\n|-\n| 2015-2016 || ''[[Amour (musical)|Le Passe-Muraille]]'' || Prosecutor ||\n|-\n|}\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" \n|-\n! Year \n! Award\n! Category\n! Nominated work\n! Result\n|-\n| 2012 || [[2012 SBS Drama Awards|SBS Drama Awards]] || Special Award, Actor in a Miniseries || ''[[The Chaser (TV series)|The Chaser]]'' || {{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" |2016\n|2nd [[Scene Stealer Festival]]\n|Scene Stealer Award (Male)\n| rowspan=\"3\" |''[[Descendants of the Sun]]''\n|{{Won}}\n|-\n|[[9th Korea Drama Awards|9th]] [[Korea Drama Awards]]\n|Excellence Award, Actor\n|{{Won}}\n|-\n|[[2016 KBS Drama Awards|30th]] [[KBS Drama Awards]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" |Best Supporting Actor\n|{{Nom}}\n|-\n|2017\n|[[2017 KBS Drama Awards|31st]] [[KBS Drama Awards]]\n|''[[Mad Dog (TV series)|Mad Dog]]''\n|{{Nom}}\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|2}}\