[[supporting actor]] in numerous films and [[Korean drama|television series]], including ''[[The Man from Nowhere (2010 film)|The Man from Nowhere]]'' (2010), ''[[The Chaser (TV series)|The Chaser]]'' (2012), ''[[Gu Family Book]]'' (2013), and ''[[The Suspect (2013 South Korean film)|The Suspect]]'' (2013).<ref>{{cite web|last1=Sunwoo|first1=Carla|title=Actor Jo Jae-yun is single no more|url=http://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/news/article/Article.aspx?aid=2956843|website=[[Korea JoongAng Daily]]|accessdate=5 February 2015|date=26 July 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Kim|first1=Dong-joo|title=Cho Jae Yoon highly compliments Suzy|url=http://en.starnnews.com/news/index.html?no=204367|website=StarN News|accessdate=5 February 2015|date=13 June 2013}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Hong|first1=Grace Danbi|title=Lee Seung Gi and miss A's Suzy Send Birthday Messages to Jo Jae Yoon's Ailing Father|url=http://mwave.interest.me/enewsworld/en/article/38340/lee-seung-gi-and-miss-a-suzy-help-co-star|website=enewsWorld|accessdate=5 February 2015|date=12 June 2013}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Sunwoo|first1=Carla|title=Gong Yoo a ''Suspect'' in his first action role|url=http://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/news/article/article.aspx?aid=2981961|website=[[Korea JoongAng Daily]]|accessdate=5 February 2015|date=13 December 2013}}</ref> Jo also appears in the variety-[[reality show]] ''[[Animals (South Korean TV series)|Animals]]'' (2015).<ref>{{cite web|last1=Ahn|first1=Woorim|title=Yoon Do Hyun Reveals A Photo With The Casts of MBC ''Animals''|url=http://www.bntnews.co.uk/app/news.php?nid=17225|website=BNTNews|accessdate=5 February 2015|date=14 January 2015}}</ref>\n\n==Filmography==\n\n===Film===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year \n! Title\n! Role\n|-\n| 2003 || ''[[Please Teach Me English]]'' || Manager Hong\n|-\n| 2004 || ''[[Au Revoir, UFO]]'' || Employee at last stop\n|-\n| 2005 || ''[[The President's Last Bang]]'' || Security guard\n|-\n| rowspan=2|2006 || ''[[Love Me No